code: @Override protected NodeInfo<OrderBy> info() {     return NodeInfo.create(this, OrderBy::new, child(), order). }

@Override public boolean equals(Object obj) {     if (this == obj) {         return true.     }     if (obj == null || getClass() != obj.getClass()) {         return false.     }     OrderBy other = (OrderBy) obj.     return Objects.equals(order, other.order) && Objects.equals(child(), other.child()). }
